{
  "texts": [
    "Overall, the survey (►Supplementary Table S4, available in the online version only) results indicated a high level of user satisfaction.",
    "Most respondents found the system easy to use and the majority expressed confidence in their ability to use the system without technical support.",
    "The integration of different functions within the system was well received and users reported that they could learn to use the system quickly.",
    "Users found the process of entering new subjects, visits, and observations simple and straightforward.",
    "The layout was considered user-friendly and provided a good overview of relevant data."
  ]
}